sources.description:
What Horror Awaits in the Tomb of the Living Dead?
A couple, lost in thick fog, take refuge in an old mansion next to a cemetery. Strange things start to happen.

Original title: La mansion de la niebla  AKA: The Murder Mansion / Maniac Mansion

This film is available with English, Italian & Spanish dubbed audio. Go to settings ⚙️ to select your subtitle /audio options.

Director: Francisco Lara Polop
Writers: Luis G. de Blain, Antonio Troiso
Stars: Ida Galli, Analía Gadé, Lisa Leonardi
Genres: Spanish cinema, Horror, Thriller
